b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":2384,"category_name":"News","pr_category_id":"1","title_name":"Regarding a Network Connection Issue [Update]","message":"<div><span style=\\"color: rgb(41, 105, 176);\\"><strong>[Addendum <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1627372800\\"><\/span>]<\/strong><\/span><br>Players who had purchased the 7-Day Pack (Double Bonus) did not receive the extra amount of items they should have obtained.<br><br>We will send these items to all affected players starting <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1627372800\\"><\/span>.<br><br>Thank you for your patience.<\/div><div><br><\/div><hr><div><span style=\\"color: rgb(41, 105, 176);\\"><strong>[Addendum <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1627297200\\"><\/span>]<\/strong><\/span><br>In relation to this issue, the following issues occurred between approximately <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1627281000\\"><\/span> and <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1627281300\\"><\/span>.<br><br>\\u25a0Details of the issues<br>\\u30fbWhen playing any quest besides the Trials of the Mighty quests that provide a daily bonus, an error occurred which made it impossible to clear the quest.<br>\\u30fbThe daily bonus for Trials of the Mighty quests could not be obtained even when clearing these quests.<br><br>These issues have now been resolved.<br><br>We have also sent all players who cleared Trials of the Mighty quests while these issues were occurring the daily bonus items that they should have received when clearing said quests.<br>These items can be claimed from your goodie box.<\/div><div><br><\/div><hr><div>We have confirmed that a network issue was temporarily preventing connection to the Dragalia Lost game around <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1627281000\\"><\/span>.&nbsp;<\/div><div>This issue has now been resolved.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","